# WeConnect

This is the WeConnect app api which provides a platform that brings businesses and 
individuals together. This platform will create awareness for businesses and gives 
the users the ability to write reviews about the businesses they have interacted with.

# Group Businesses

## Businesses Collection [api/v1/businesses]

### Get All Businesses [GET api/v1/businesses]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - businesses (array[Business])
            

### Get A Single Business [GET api/v1/businesses/{id}]
+ Parameter
    + id: `1` - The ID of the Business

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - Include Business

### Register A New Business [POST api/v1/businesses]
+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - businesses (array[Business])

### Update a Businesses [PUT api/v1/businesses/{id}]
+ Parameter
    + id: `1` - The ID of the Business

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - businesses (array[Business])

### Delete a Businesses [DELETE api/v1/businesses/{id}]
+ Parameter
    + id: `1` - The ID of the Business

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - Include Review


# Group Reviews

## Reviews Collection [api/v1/businesses/{id}/reviews]

### Get A Single Business Reviews [GET api/v1/businesses/{id}/reviews]
+ Parameter
    + id: `1` - The ID of the Business

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - reviews (array[Review])

### Post A Business Review [POST api/v1/businesses/{id}/reviews]
+ Parameter
    + id: `1` - The ID of the Business

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - review (array[Review])

# Group Filter

## Filter Collection [api/v1/businesses]

### Filter Businesses By Location [POST api/v1/businesses/location/:location]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - businesses (array[Business])

### Filter Businesses By Category [POST api/v1/businesses/category/:category]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - businesses (array[Business])

# Group Authentication

## Authentication Collection [api/v1/businesses]

### Create A New User [POST api/v1/auth/signup]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - user (array[User])

### Login A New User [POST api/v1/auth/login]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        - user (array[User])

# Data Structures

## Business (object)
- id: `1` (number) - The ID of the business
- name: `ABC Ltd` (string) - The Name of the business
- description: `We are the best at what we do` (string) - The Description of the business
- location: `Lagos` (string) - The Location of the business
- category: `Fashion` (string) - The Category of the business

## Review (object)
- id: `1` (number) - The ID of the review
- content: `Good customer service` (string) - The Content of the review
- user: `John Doe` (string) - The Author of the review
- rating: `4` (number) - The Rating of the business

## User (object)
- id: `1` (number) - The ID of the user
- email: `dummy1@dummy.com` (string) - The Email of the user
- password: `test` (string) - The Password of the user